declared%20before%20June%2030%2C%20or%20forgo%20the%20compensatory%20marks%20given%20for%20the%20loss%20of%20time.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThe%20exam%20was%20held%20first%20on%20May%205%20and%20its%20results%20were%20declared%20on%20June%204%2C%20ahead%20of%20its%20scheduled%20announcement%20date%20of%20June%2014.%20Protests%20were%20held%20alleging%20irregularities%20and%20paper%20leaks%20as%20the%20results%20showed%20that%20as%20many%20as%2067%20students%20had%20topped%20the%20exam%20with%20a%20perfect%20score%20of%20720.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EEducation%20Minister%20Dharmendra%20Pradhan%20had%20on%20Thursday%20ruled%20out%20cancellation%20of%20NEET%2C%20saying%20he%20cannot%20jeopardise%20careers%20of%20lakhs%20of%20students%20who%20cleared%20the%20exam%20rightfully%20because%20of%20%26quot%3Bisolated%20incidents%20of%20malpractices%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThe%20Centre%20on%20Saturday%20replaced%20National%20Testing%20Agency%20Director%20General%20Subodh%20Singh%20and%20set%20up%20a%20seven-member%20panel%20headed%20by%20former%20ISRO%20chief%20K%20Radhakrishnan%20to%20review%20the%20agency's%20functioning%20and%20recommend%20exam%20reforms.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThe%20government%20has%20also%20operationalised%20a%20stringent%20law%20that%20aims%20to%20curb%20malpractices%20and%20irregularities%20in%20competitive%20examinations.%20A%20maximum%20jail%20term%20of%2010%20years%20and%20a%20fine%20of%20up%20to%20Rs%201%20crore%20for%20offenders%20are%20some%20of%20the%20tough%20measures%20under%20the%20law.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EAmid%20an%20escalating%20row%20over%20the%20National%20Eligibility-cum-Entrance%20(NEET)-Undergraduate%20exam%202024%2C%20the%20Health%20Ministry%20has%20decided%20to%20postpone%20the%20NEET-Post%20Graduate%20exams%20which%20were%20to%20be%20held%20today.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%26quot%3BTaking%20into%20consideration%20the%20recent%20incidents%20of%20allegations%20regarding%20the%20integrity%20of%20certain%20competitive%20examinations%2C%20the%20Ministry%20of%20Health%20has%20decided%20to%20undertake%20a%20thorough%20assessment%20of%20the%20robustness%20of%20processes%20of%20NEET-PG%20Entrance%20Examination%2C%20conducted%20by%20National%20Board%20of%20Examination%20for%20medical%20students%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20the%20Ministry.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThe%20Congress%20on%20Friday%20held%20protests%20across%20the%20country%20over%20alleged%20irregularities%20in%20the%20medical%20entrance%20exam%20with%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20saying%20he%20will%20raise%20the%20issue%20in%20parliament%20and%20the%20opposition%20will%20put%20pressure%20on%20the%20government%20to%20ensure%20justice%20for%20students.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fol%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1719105420000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-06%2Fbq3lj698_neet-1200_625x300_22_June_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fneet-ug-retest-news-as-exam-row-escalates-1-500-students-to-appear-for-neet-ug-retest-today-5948196%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22It's%20exam%20time%20again.%20The%20National%20Eligibility-cum-Entrance%20(NEET-UG)%20retest%20for%201%2C563%20candidates%20is%20being%20reconducted%20today%20after%20the%20testing%20agency%20withdrew%20the%20grace%20marks%20awarded%20to%20them%20to%20make%20up%20for%20the%20loss%20of%20time.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fneet-ug-retest-news-as-exam-row-escalates-1-500-students-to-appear-for-neet-ug-retest-today-5948196%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fneet-ug-retest-news-as-exam-row-escalates-1-500-students-to-appear-for-neet-ug-retest-today-5948196%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fneet-ug-retest-news-as-exam-row-escalates-1-500-students-to-appear-for-neet-ug-retest-today-5948196%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Two%20dead%2C%2017%20injured%20in%20separate%