0Revanna's%20Brother%20For%20Sexually%20Assaulting%20Worker%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EJD(S)%20MLC%20Suraj%20Revanna%20was%20booked%20on%20Saturday%20for%20allegedly%20sexually%20assaulting%20a%20party%20worker%20a%20few%20days%20ago%2C%20police%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChethan%20K%20S%20(27)%20had%20complained%20to%20the%20police%20that%20Suraj%20Revanna%2C%20the%20eldest%20son%20of%20Holenarasipura%20MLA%20H%20D%20Revanna%2C%20sexually%20assaulted%20him%20at%20his%20farmhouse%20in%20Ghannikada%20in%20Holenarasipura%20Taluk%20on%20June%2016%20evening.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBased%20on%20the%20complaint%2C%20the%20Holenarasipura%20police%20registered%20a%20case%20against%20the%20JD(S)%20MLC%20under%20IPC%20sections%20377%20(unnatural%20sex)%20and%20506%20(criminal%20intimidation)%20late%20on%20Saturday%20evening.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20Suraj%20Revanna%20(37)%2C%20the%20grandson%20of%20former%20prime%20minister%20H%20D%20Deve%20Gowda%20and%20the%20nephew%20of%20Union%20Minister%20H%20D%20Kumaraswamy%2C%20has%20categorically%20refuted%20the%20charge.%20Instead%2C%20he%20has%20alleged%20that%20Chethan%20filed%20a%20false%20complaint%20to%20extort%20Rs%205%20crore%20from%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPolice%20have%20not%20yet%20arrested%20Suraj%20Revanna.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20Friday%2C%20police%20registered%20a%20case%20of%20extortion%20against%20Chethan%20on%20a%20complaint%20by%20Suraj%20Revanna's%20close%20aide%20Shivakumar.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShivakumar%20has%20alleged%20that%20Chethan%20was%20trying%20to%20extort%20money%20from%20Suraj%20Revanna%20by%20threatening%20to%20lodge%20a%20false%20case%20of%20sexual%20assault%20against%20him.%20It%20has%20been%20alleged%20that%20Chethan%20demanded%20Rs%205%20crore%20from%20Suraj%20Revanna%20and%20later%20it%20was%20reduced%20to%20Rs%202%20crore.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESuraj%20is%20the%20elder%20brother%20of%20former%20Hassan%20MP%20Prajwal%20Revanna%20who%20is%20in%20police%20custody%20for%20allegedly%20sexua