%20by%20the%20National%20Board%20of%20Examination%20for%20medical%20students.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20has%20accordingly%20been%20decided%2C%20as%20a%20precautionary%20measure%2C%20to%20postpone%20the%20NEET-PG%20scheduled%20to%20be%20held%20tomorrow%20(June%2023).%20Fresh%20date%20of%20this%20examination%20will%20be%20notified%20at%20the%20earliest%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20Health%20Ministry%20said%2C%20adding%20it%20%26quot%3Bsincerely%20regrets%20the%20inconvenience%20caused%20to%20students%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20government%20said%20the%20decision%20was%20taken%20in%20the%20best%20interests%20of%20students%20and%20to%20maintain%20the%20sanctity%20of%20examination.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAn%20hour%20before%20the%20announcement%20of%20the%20exam%20postponement%20came%2C%20the%20government%20issued%20an%20order%20that%20said%20it%20has%20replaced%20the%20chief%20of%20the%20National%20Testing%20Agency%20(NTA)%2C%20which%20conducts%20the%20NEET-UG%20and%20UGC-NET.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESubodh%20Kumar%20Singh%2C%20who%20was%20NTA%20director%20general%2C%20has%20been%20replaced%20by%20retired%20Indian%20Administration%20Service%20(IAS)%20officer%20Pradeep%20Singh%20Kharola.%20The%20move%20is%20significant%20as%20it%20shows%20the%20government%20is%20cracking%20down%20on%20NTA%20officials.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20the%20parliament%20session%20beginning%20soon%2C%20the%20Centre%20is%20bracing%20to%20face%20an%20onslaught%20of%20questions%20on%20the%20controversies%20surrounding%20these%20key%20exams%20for%20entry%20into%20medical%20and%20higher%20education%20teaching%20positions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%20on%20Saturday%2C%20the%20Education%20Ministry%20formed%20a%20high-level%20committee%20of%20experts%20to%20make%20recommendations%20on%20reform%20in%20the%20mechanism%20of%20the%20examination%20process%2C%20improvement%20in%20data%20security%20protocols%2C%20structure%20and%20functioning%20of%20the%20NTA.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20UGC-NET%20wa