20Tour%20show%20at%20Wembley%20Stadium.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20World%20Desk%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Ftaylor-swifts-epic-selfie-with-prince-william-has-a-hidden-message%2Farticleshow%2F111195524.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia-indiatimes-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Ftaylor-swifts-epic-selfie-with-prince-william-has-a-hidden-message%2Famp_articleshow%2F111195524.cms%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Ftaylor-swifts-epic-selfie-with-prince-william-has-a-hidden-message%2Famp_articleshow%2F111195524.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Centre%20Removes%20Exam%20Body%20Chief%2C%20CBI%20To%20Probe%20NEET-UG%20Irregularities%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EFacing%20protests%20in%20several%20parts%20of%20the%20country%20as%20well%20as%20attacks%20from%20the%20opposition%2C%20the%20Centre%20has%20removed%20the%20chief%20of%20the%20National%20Testing%20Agency%20(NTA)%20from%20his%20post%20amid%20the%20controversy%20over%20the%20alleged%20irregularities%20in%20NEET-UG%20and%20the%20cancellation%20of%20the%20UGC-NET%20Exam.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20statement%20on%20Saturday%2C%20the%20Ministry%20of%20Personnel%20announced%20that%20Subodh%20Kumar%20Singh%2C%20who%20was%20the%20director%20general%20of%20the%20NTA%2C%20has%20been%20replaced%20by%20retired%20Indian%20Administration%20Service%20(IAS)%20officer%20Pradeep%20Singh%20Kharola.%20Mr%20Kharola%20is%20the%20Chairman%20and%20Managing%20Editor%20of%20the%20India%20Trade%20Promotion%20Organisation%20and%20has%20been%20given%20additional%20charge%20as%20the%20director%20general%20of%20the%20NTA%20%26quot%3Btill%20the%20appointment%20of%20a%20regular%20incumbent%20or%20until%20further%20orders%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20move%20comes%20hours%20after%20the%20government%20constituted%20a%20committee%20which%20will%20give%20recommendations%20to%20improve%20the%20functioning%20of%20the%20agency%20and%20a%20day%20before%20around%201%2C500%20students%20who%20had%20been%20given%20grace%20marks%20for%20NEET-UG%20are%20scheduled%20to%20take%20a%20retest.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20CSIR%20UGC%20NET%20exam%20-%20scheduled%20to%20be%20held%20from%20June%2025%20to%20June%2027%20-%20also%20had%20to%20be%20postponed%20due%20to%20%26quot%3Blogistical%20reasons%26quot%3B%20on%20Friday%20and%20the%20NEET-PG%20exam%2C%20slated%20to%20be%20held%20on%20Sunday%2C%20was%20rescheduled%20late%20on%20Saturday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECapping%20a%20day%20of%20fast-moving%20developments%2C%20the%20government%20also%20handed%20over%20the%20probe%20into%20the%20alleged%20irregularities%2C%20including%20the%20paper%20leaks%2C%20in%20the%20NEET-UG%20exam%20to%20the%20CBI%20on%20Saturday.%20The%20agency%20is%20also%20probing%20the%20alleged%20leaks%20that%20led%20to%20the%20cancellation%20of%20the%20UGC%20NET%20exam.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESources%20have%20told%20NDTV%20that%20the%20repeated%20allegations%20of%20leaks%20in%20exams%20conducted%20by%20the%20NTA%20and%20the%20inconvenience%20caused%20to%20students%2C%20as%20well%20as%20the%20outpouring%20of%20anger%20among%20them%2C%20had%20made%20Mr%20Singh's%20position%20tenuous.%20Pressure%20from%20a%20resurgent%20opposition%20as%20well%20as%20adverse%20remarks%20by%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20against%20the%20NTA%20also%20played%20a%20role%20in%20the%20decision%20to%20remove%20the%20exam%20body%20chief.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20move%20is%20also%20part%20of%20a%20promised%20overhaul%20of%20the%20National%20Testing%20Agency%2C%20which%20has%20been%20spoken%20about%20by%20Education%20Minister%20Dharmendra%20Pradhan%20as%20well.%20Sources%20said%20that%2C%20at%20a%20recent%20Cabinet%20meeting%2C%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20had%20asked%20Mr%20Pradhan%20to%20take%20action%2C%20and%20the%20crackdown%20has%20now%20begun.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EPunishing%20The%20Guilty%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20priority%20for%20the%20government%20now%2C%20they%20said%2C%20is%20to%20get%20to%20the%20bottom%20of%20the%20alleged%20paper%20leaks%20and%20bring%20the%20guilty%20to%20book.%20This%20is%20especially%20important%20since%20the%20NTA%20organises%20several%20key%20examinations%2C%20including%20the%20NEET%20and%20JEE%2C%20in%20which%20lakhs%20of%20students%20appear.%20The%20Supreme%20Court%20is%20also%20scheduled%20to%20hear%20petitions%20on%20the%20issue%20on%20July%208.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%20on%20Saturday%2C%20the%20government%20constituted%20a%20seven-member%20committee%20to%20look%20at%20ways%20of%20improving%20the%20functioning%20of%20the%20NTA.%20The%20panel%20will%20be%20led%20by%20Dr%20K%20Radhakrishnan%2C%20a%20former%20ISRO%20chief%20and%20the%20current%20chairperson%20of%20the%20board%20of%20governors%20of%20IIT%20Kanpur%2C%20and%20will%20have%20former%20AIIMS%20director%20Dr%20Randeep%20Guleria%20as%20one%20of%20the%20members.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20the%20committee%20was%20formed%2C%20Mr%20Pradhan%20said%20it%20was%20the%20first%20in%20a%20series%20of%20steps%20to%20improve%20the%20efficiency%20of%20the%20examination%20process.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BTransparent%2C%20tamper-free%20and%20zero-error%20examinations%20is%20a%20commitment.%20Setting%20up%20of%20the%20high-level%20committee%20of%20experts%20is%20the%20first%20of%20a%20series%20of%20step%20to%20improve%20efficiency%20of%20the%20examination%20process%2C%20put%20an%20end%20to%20all%20possible%20malpractices%2C%20strengthen%20data%20security%20protocols%20and%20overhaul%20and%20reform%20the%20NTA.%20Student%20interests%20and%20their%20bright%20future%20will%20always%20be%20our%20govt's%20top%20priority%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20posted%20on%20X.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EMess%20Gets%20Messier%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENearly%2024%20lakh%20students%20had%20appeared%20for%20the%20NEET-UG%202024%20for%20undergraduate%20medical%20courses%2C%20which%20is%20conducted%20by%20the%20National%20Testing%20Agency%2C%20on%20May%205.%20The%20results%20were%20announced%20on%20June%204%2C%2010%20days%20before%20schedule%2C%20but%20allegations%20of%20question%20paper%20leaks%20and%20grace%20marks%20to%20over%201%2C500%20students%20triggered%20protests.%20Cases%20were%20also%20filed%20in%20courts%2C%20including%20the%20Supreme%20Court%2C%20which%20has%20rapped%20the%20NTA.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20Wednesday%2C%20the%20Education%20Ministry%20had%20cancelled%20the%20UGC-NET%20exam%2C%20also%20conducted%20by%20the%20NTA%2C%20just%20a%20day%20after%20it%20was%20held.%20Over%209%20lakh%20candidates%20had%20appeared%20for%20the%20exam%2C%20which%20is%20held%20for%20Assistant%20Professor%20posts%20in%20universities%20and%20colleges%20and%20to%20determine%20eligibility%20for%20junior%20research%20fellowships.%20Mr%20Pradhan%20had%20said%20the%20UGC%20chairman%20had%20received%20information%20from%20the%20cyber%20crime%20team%20in%20the%20Home%20Ministry%20about%20questions%20being%20on%20the%20darknet.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20CSIR%20UGC%20NET%20-%20similar%20to%20the%20UGC%20NET%2C%20but%20for%20science%20students%20-%20was%20postponed%20on%20Friday%20and%20NEET%20PG%20was%20pushed%20back%20on%20Saturday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20INDIA%20alliance%2C%20which%20won%20232%20seats%20in%20the%20recently%20held%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections%20and%20kept%20the%20BJP%20from%20winning%20a%20majority%20on%20its%20own%2C%20has%20also%20been%20attacking%20the%20Centre%20relentlessly%20over%20the%20issue.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20Saturday%2C%20Congress%20leader%20Priyanka%20Gandhi%20Vadra%2C%20who%20is%20gearing%20up%20to%20make%20her%20electoral%20debut%2C%20posted%20on%20X%3A%20%26quot%3BUnder%20the%20BJP%20government%2C%20NTA%20has%20become%20a%20No%20Trust%20Agency%20and%20examinations%20have%20become%20a%20terrible%20tragedy.%20Lakhs%20of%20hardworking%20children%20and%20parents%