li%20official%20figures.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIsrael's%20retaliatory%20offensive%20has%20killed%20at%20least%2037%2C431%20people%20in%20Gaza%2C%20also%20mostly%20civilians%2C%20according%20to%20the%20territory's%20health%20ministry.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20were%20all%20targeted%20(on%20October%207)%20and%20I%20don't%20want%20to%20be%20taken%20by%20surprise%2C%20so%20I'm%20trying%20to%20defend%20myself%2C%26quot%3B%20Gonen%20said%20after%20the%20class%2C%20an%20obligatory%20step%20for%20acquiring%20a%20permit.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E100%2C000%20armed%20civilians%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20immediate%20trigger%20for%20the%20surge%20in%20gun%20buying%20was%20the%20Hamas%20attack%2C%20Ben%20Gvir%20was%20already%20pledging%20to%20reform%20firearms%20legislation%20when%20he%20became%20security%20minister%20in%20late%202022.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20promised%20to%20raise%20the%20number%20of%20civilians%20holding%20weapons%20and%20%26quot%3Bincrease%20self-defence%20capacity%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUnder%20Ben%20Gvir%2C%20the%20process%20for%20getting%20a%20gun%20license%20has%20been%20sped%20up%2C%20with%20Israeli%20media%20reporting%20that%20in%20the%20immediate%20aftermath%20of%20the%20Hamas%20attack%20the%20authorities%20were%20often%20clearing%20hundreds%20of%20permits%20per%20day.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEligibility%20criteria%20for%20gun%20ownership%20in%20Israel%20now%20include%20being%20a%20citizen%20or%20permanent%20resident%20over%20the%20age%20of%2018%2C%20having%20a%20basic%20command%20of%20Hebrew%20and%20medical%20clearance.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20full%20list%20of%20requirements%20makes%20it%20nearly%20impossible%20for%20non-Jews%20to%20obtain%20a%20permit.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20March%2C%20Ben%20Gvir%2C%20who%20is%20himself%20a%20settler%20in%20the%20West%20Bank%2C%20hailed%20civilian%20weapon%20ownership%20passing%20the%20100%2C000%20mark%2C%20while%20showing%20off%20his%20own%20gun%20at%20a%20rally.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20his%20rush%20to%20put%20deadly%20arms%20into%20the%20hands%20of%20ordinary%20Israelis%20has%20drawn%20criticism%20too.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Gun%20Free%20Kitchen%20Tables%20Coalition%2C%20an%20Israeli%20initiative%20founded%20by%20feminist%20activists%2C%20condemned%20the%20civilian%20arms%20race.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20%26quot%3Ba%20strategy%20of%20far-right%20settlers%20to%20consider%20the%20arming%20of%20women%20to%20be%20a%20feminist%20act%26quot%3B%2C%20a%20spokesperson%20for%20the%20group%20of%2018%20organisations%20told%20AFP.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20increase%20of%20weapons%20in%20the%20civilian%20space%20leads%20to%20an%20increase%20in%20violence%20and%20murder%20against%20women.%20It's%20time%20for%20the%20state%20to%20understand%20that%20individual%20safety%20is%20its%20responsibility.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E'More%20safe'%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECommunity%20manager%20Yahel%20Reznik%2C%2024%2C%20said%20she%20now%20felt%20%26quot%3Ba%20lot%20more%20safe%26quot%3B%20in%20Ariel%2C%20which%20sits%20three%20kilometres%20north%20of%20the%20Palestinian%20city%20of%20Salfit.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThanks%20to%20my%20training%20I%20will%20be%20able%20to%20defend%20myself%20and%20protect%20others%26quot%3B%20from%20an%20attack%2C%20she%20told%20AFP.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EViolence%20in%20the%20West%20Bank%2C%20which%20was%20already%20rising%20before%20the%20war%2C%20has%20surged%20since%20October%207.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20least%20549%20Palestinians%20have%20been%20killed%20by%20Israeli%20settlers%20and%20troops%20across%20the%20West%20Bank%20since%20the%20start%20of%20the%20Gaza%20war%2C%20according%20to%20the%20Palestinian%20Authority.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAttacks%20by%20Palestinians%20have%20killed%20at%20least%2014%20Israelis%2C%20according%20to%20an%20AFP%20tally%20of%20Israeli%20official%20figures.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20surge%20in%20gun%20ownership%20is%20not%20limited%20to%20West%20Bank%20settlers.%20In%20the%20Israeli%20coastal%20city%20of%20Netanya%2C%20just%20north%20of%20Tel%20Aviv%2C%20Corine%20Nissim%20said%20she%20never%20leaves%20home%20without%20her%20gun.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%2042-year-old%20English%20teacher%20walked%20her%20three%20children%20to%20the%20park%20with%20a%209mm%20Smith%20%26amp%3B%20Wesson%20sticking%20out%20the%20back%20of%20her%20trousers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAfter%20October%207%2C%20I%20think%20like%20most%20people%20in%20Israel%2C%20I%20realised%20that%20the%20only%20person%20I%20can%20trust%20is%20myself%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20told%20AFP%2C%20adding%20she%20bought%20a%20gun%20not%20to%20feel%20%26quot%3Bhelpless%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20worst%20scenario%20that%20was%20going%20through%20my%20head%20was%20that%2C%20of%20course%2C%20terrorists%20attack%20me%20and%20my%20family%20in%20our%20own%20house%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20mother%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHer%20decision%20to%20own%20a%20gun%20initially%20surprised%20some%20in%20the%20seaside%20town%20known%20for%20its%20tranquillity%20and%20safety%2C%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BPeople%20watched%20me%20and%20said%2C%20'This%20is%20so%20surreal%20to%20see%20you%20like%20this%20with%20a%20gun%20and%20with%20the%20baby'%26quot%3B%20said%20Nissim.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%2C%20she%20said%2C%20others%20started%20to%20agree%20with%20her%20and%20said%20they%20would%20follow%20suit.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMany%20women%20told%20me%3A%20'I'm%20going%20to%20do%20it.%20I'm%20going%20to%20get%20a%20gun%20as%20well.'%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1719055380000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-06%2Fvrctg0e_israeli-women-get-guns_625x300_22_June_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworl