20all%20tough%20questions.%20It%20is%20difficult%20to%20answer%20right%20now.%20All%20I%20can%20say%20right%20now%20is%20that%20I%20am%20happy%20being%20here.%20Just%20finished%20a%20brilliant%20journey%20with%20Kolkata%20Knight%20Riders%20let's%20enjoy%20that.%20I%20am%20in%20a%20very%20happy%20space%20right%20now%2C%26quot%3B%20Gambhir%20said%20during%20an%20event%20in%20Kolkata.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20left-handed%20opener%20served%20as%20Kolkata%20Knight%20Riders'%20team%20mentor%20in%20the%20Indian%20Premier%20League%202024.%20The%20return%20of%20the%20franchise's%20former%20captain%20saw%20the%20Knights%20lift%20their%20third%20IPL%20trophy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20talked%20about%20his%20coaching%20philosophy%20and%20emphasized%20the%20need%20to%20treat%20everyone%20equally%20rather%20than%20focus%20on%20a%20couple%20of%20individual%20players.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20a%20team%20sport%2C%20it's%20the%20team%20that%20matters%20the%20most.%20It's%20the%20team%20that%20is%20the%20most%20important%20ingredient%20in%20that%20organisation.%20Individuals%20do%20play%20a%20role%2C%20and%20individuals%20do%20contribute%2C%20but%20ultimately%2C%20if%2011%20people%20are%20treated%20equally%2C%20if%2011%20people%20have%20equal%20respect%2C%20if%20everyone%20is%20treated%20equally%2C%20given%20the%20same%20respect%2C%20same%20responsibility%2C%20given%20the%20same%20honour%2C%20you%20will%20achieve%20an%20unbelievable%20amount%20of%20success.%20You%20cannot%20have%20discrimination%20in%20a%20set-up%20or%20in%20an%20organisation%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Indian%20team%20is%20currently%20thriving%20in%20the%20T20%20World%20Cup%20after%20they%20began%20their%20Super%208%20campaign%20with%20a%2047-run%20win%20over%20Afghanistan.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Rohit%20Sharma-led%20unbeaten%20side%20will%20face%20Bangladesh%20on%20Saturday%20at%20Sir%20Vivian%20Richards%20Stadium%20in%20Antigua.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(This%20story%20has%20not%