IAS-Ashish-_11zon-1718972552-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2FIAS-Ashish-_11zon-1718972552-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2FIAS-Ashish-_11zon-1718972552-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2FIAS-Ashish-_11zon-1718972552-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-353822%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EIt%20was%20in%20his%20fifth%20attempt%20that%20Ashish%20finally%20achieved%20success.%20%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E3.%20Set%20a%20timer%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIn%20place%20of%20studying%20for%2012%20or%2014%20hours%2C%20I%20focussed%20on%20studying%20dedicatedly%20for%20seven%20hours%20daily.%20I%20started%20using%20a%20stopwatch%20for%20focused%20studies.%20I%20would%20spend%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20time%20gossiping%20with%20my%20parents%2C%20walking%20in%20the%20park%2C%20and%20listening%20to%20music%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Ashish.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E4.%20Source%20optimisation%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20IAS%20officer%20advises%20aspirants%20to%20minimise%20source%20material.%20%E2%80%9CRely%20on%20one%20or%20two%20sources%20that%20help%20you%20complete%20the%20syllabus%20for%20a%20subject.%20Do%20not%20get%20distracted%20by%20multiple%20sources.%20Initially%2C%20I%20was%20also%20in%20the%20trap%20of%20purchasing%20multiple%20books%2C%20but%20it%E2%80%99s%20better%20to%20fix%20your%20sources%20and%20study%20from%20the%20same%20source%20again%20and%20again%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20advises.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESharing%20his%20source%20material%2C%20Ashish%20informs%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%20studied%20NCERTs%20from%20Standard%206%20to%2012%20for%20almost%20all%20subjects%20to%20develop%20foundational%20knowledge.%20I%20referred%20to%20standard%20books%20like%20Laxmikant%2