20parents%20lived%20in%20a%20village%20all%20their%20lives.%20So%2C%20in%20many%20ways%2C%20sport%20was%20a%20big%20part%20of%20their%20lives.%20And%20when%20I%20was%20five%20years%20old%2C%20it%20became%20a%20big%20part%20of%20mine%20too.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2Fhetal-dave-1718375371.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Hetal%20Dave%2C%20India's%20only%20professional%20female%20sumo%20wrestler%20with%20her%20mother%2C%20father%20and%20brother%2C%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2Fhetal-dave-1718375371.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2Fhetal-dave-1718375371-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2Fhetal-dave-1718375371-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2Fhetal-dave-1718375371-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2Fhetal-dave-1718375371-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-353187%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EHetal%20Dave%2C%20India%E2%80%99s%20only%20professional%20female%20sumo%20wrestler%20with%20her%20mother%2C%20father%20and%20brother%2C%20Picture%20source%3A%20Hetal%20%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20while%20the%20two%20generations%20bonded%20over%20this%20passion%20for%20sports%2C%20circumstances%20distinguished%20the%20fortune%20of%20pursuing%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHetal%20explains%2C%20%E2%80%9CIn%20the%20village%2C%20my%20parents%20did%20not%20have%20much%20exposure%20to%20facilities%20or%20opportunities.%20Later%20on%2C%20family%20responsibilities%20took%20over%20and%20they%20